{"product_id":"al-saalim-premium-attar-combo-pack-pack-of-3-aseel-white-musk-signature-roll-on-6ml-each-alcohol-free","title":"Al-Saalim Premium Attar Combo Pack (Pack of 3 – Aseel, White Musk \u0026 Signature) | Roll On 6ml Each | Alcohol Free","description":"\u003cp\u003eEnjoy a luxurious fragrance experience with the Al-Saalim Premium Attar Combo Pack, featuring three unique and elegant attars – Aseel, White Musk, and Signature. This special combo is crafted for fragrance lovers who want a perfect blend of traditional richness and modern freshness.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eEach attar in this combo offers a distinct aroma, giving you the flexibility to choose a fragrance based on your mood, occasion, or preference. These alcohol-free attars are gentle on the skin and provide a smooth, long-lasting scent throughout the day.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis combo is perfect for personal use, gifting, or building your premium attar collection.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCombo Includes\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e✔ Aseel Attar – Rich, warm \u0026amp; traditional oriental fragrance\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e✔ White Musk Attar – Clean, soft \u0026amp; refreshing musk aroma\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e✔ Signature Attar – Classic, smooth \u0026amp; premium elegant fragrance\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eKey Features\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePack of 3 Premium Attars\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eQuantity: 6ml Each Bottle\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAlcohol Free \u0026amp; Skin Friendly\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eLong Lasting Fragrance\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePremium Roll-On Glass Bottles\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSuitable for Men \u0026amp; Women\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePerfect for Daily Wear \u0026amp; Special Occasions\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIdeal Luxury Gift Set\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWhy Choose This Combo\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThree unique fragrances in one pack\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBalanced combination of fresh, warm, and elegant aromas\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePremium quality traditional attars\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eGreat value for money\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHow to Use\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eApply lightly on pulse points such as wrists, neck, or behind the ears for a long-lasting fragrance.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"AL-SAALIM PERFUMES","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50474789044471,"sku":null,"price":479.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0923\/0755\/4551\/files\/BFB62201-2C2C-452A-9A17-C5DA96A81EEA.png?v=1777870797","url":"https:\/\/alsaalimperfume.shop\/products\/al-saalim-premium-attar-combo-pack-pack-of-3-aseel-white-musk-signature-roll-on-6ml-each-alcohol-free","provider":"AL-SAALIM PERFUMES","version":"1.0","type":"link"}